  m_text: "Detective Macklin, now in his later years, was once a mechanic for Flotilla
    City #7. Due to a rare genetic autoimmune disease that developed in his 30\u2019s,
    his body could no longer withstand the harsh environments of the maintenance
    decks, and was forced to retire. Out of fear of being disposed of by Omniworks
    since he no longer had a purpose, he joined the Detective Corp, one of the most
    dangerous jobs in the entire city.\r\n"
